 We founded Ava Cyber in 2016 and Ava Video in 2018 and the two companies merged in 2020 to become a unified security provider with extensive capital investment from Ubon Partners. About this position
 We are looking for highly technical Cyber Security Analyst to join our commercial team in locations across the US.
 Our Cyber Security Analysts are a critical part of our sales process, working side by side with a very professional sales team. Analysts evangelize the threat landscape as observed by Ava Reveal. An ideal candidate is familiar with Threat Hunting and can investigate threats in dynamic environments. This role encourages creativity, problem solving and attention to detail within customer environments.
 
 Your Job: 
Investigating customer environments for potential threats
 
Complete understanding of the Ava Reveal product and technical capabilities
 
Conduct effective POC Security Reviews and present your findings to the customer
 
Periodically investigate active production environments and deliver reports and remediation steps
 
Work with internal development team to relay customer feedback so we can incorporate it into our agile development process
 
Assist in training our customers
 
Stay up to date on the threat landscape
